README.md
CHANGELOG.md
LICENSE

# Ignore test files
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.js
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.js
**/test/**
**/tests/**
**/__tests__/**

# Ignore example and benchmark files
examples/**
